high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the sofa.
Take the cloth from the sofa.
Turn around move towards the sink .
Put the cloth into the sink.
Take the cloth from the sink.
Turn around put the cloth on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Take the cloth, put into the sink and put into the cloth in toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the sofa
Pick up cloth from the sofa
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right
Place cloth inside the sink and then take it out
Turn around and walk to the toilet to your left
anns.task_desc: Washing cloth on the sink and placing it on toilet

high_descs: Turn left to the couch just ahead, walking around it to its right end from the perspective of looking at it.
Pick up the pink cloth on the couch.
From the right end of the couch, go right and into the bathroom ahead.
Use the sink to wash the cloth and pick it back up.
Look to the toilet next to the sink.
Place the cloth on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Wash a cloth with water and place it on a toilet.
